  if you want to change the color of the head of the snake, change this line:

head = turtle.Turtle()
head.speed(0)
head.shape("square")
head.color("blue") <- then change this color 
head.penup()
head.goto(0,0)
head.direction = "stop"

  if you want to change the trail, change this line:
 
 new_segment = turtle.Turtle()
        new_segment.speed(0)
        new_segment.shape("square")
        new_segment.color("aqua") <- then change this color 
        new_segment.penup()
        segments.append(new_segment)
  
  if you want to change the color of the font, change this line:
  
  pen = turtle.Turtle()
pen.speed(0)
pen.shape("square")
pen.color("black") <- change this color
pen.penup()
pen.hideturtle()
pen.goto(0, 260)z
pen.write("Score: 0  High Score: 0", align="center", font=("Courier", 24, "normal"))

 if you want to change the color of the food, change this line:
 
 food = turtle.Turtle()
food.speed(0)
food.shape("square")<- you can also change the shape
food.color("red")<- change this color 
food.penup()
food.goto(0,100)

